headline: Lineworkers honored at Georgia State Capitol for Hurricane Helene response
summary: Georgia Power today joined state lawmakers for a special event at the Georgia State Capitol alongside dozens of lineworkers, representatives from the state's electric membership corporations (EMCs) and municipal electric providers.
